node.text:
Leaf Pile (Repost)
.
.
Dealing with some wrist issues rn so having to slow down on the drawing to keep them healthy! Figured I’d repost an old favourite, and where I am the air is chilly and the leaves are changing, so this seemed a fitting one! Plus good ol’ Bubs needed a feature.
.
Hope everyone has had a good start of September, and if you’re in school now best of luck with it!
.
#lilcharandthegang #comic #webcomic #fancomic #fanart #pokemon #bulbasaur #fall

node.text:
Last winter I did a Kickstarter for a Sharkpup plush toy. It exploded and I ended up making five different Sharkpup plush! With delays on the shipment getting here and fulfillment of so many orders of different types being so daunting it took a little longer to finish than originally thought. I was positively buried!
.
But it’s been absolutely darling to see people getting their Sharkpups and hearing of friends and family excited with their gifts and made all that work worth it! If you helped back the Kickstarter thank you so much for your contribution and excitement to these little guys ❤️ Fulfillment is finally wrapped up and everyone’s Sharkpups are heading home.
.
And if you only found me recently and missed out on tbe campaign, do not fear! I still have Sharkpups left and will be opening my shop for sale on ✨August 13th!✨
.
Thanks again for your support guys! It’s been exhausting and fantastic 🦈
.
#sharkpup #shark #cute #plushtoy
